The '''Vellian drop ship''' was a model of [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. One such ship was meant to be in [[Squarn's Junkyard]] when a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] were looking for spare parts to repair their [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]], but in its place was a hummock denoting a partially collapsed cargo container.

